###< symfony/messenger ###

###> doctrine/doctrine-bundle ###
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://sample:pSample1@postgres:5432/sample"
###< doctrine/doctrine-bundle ###

###> redis ###
REDIS_URL=redis://redis:6379
###> redis ###

